      "name": "Note Reading",
      "svg": "<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"390\" height=\"844\" viewBox=\"0 0 390 844\">\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"390\" height=\"844\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\"  opacity=\"1\" />\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"390\" height=\"44\" fill=\"#FAF8F4\"  opacity=\"1\" />\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"28\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">9:41</text>\n  <text x=\"370\" y=\"28\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"end\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.5\">●●●</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"73\" font-size=\"20\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">←</text>\n  <text x=\"370\" y=\"73\" font-size=\"20\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"end\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">♡</text>\n  <text x=\"342\" y=\"73\" font-size=\"20\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"end\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">⋯</text>\n  <rect x=\"20\" y=\"92\" width=\"78\" height=\"22\" fill=\"#F0E2DC\" rx=\"5\" opacity=\"1\" />\n  <text x=\"59\" y=\"107\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#C0522E\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0.5\" opacity=\"1\">PHILOSOPHY</text>\n  <text x=\"370\" y=\"107\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"end\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">12 min</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"140\" font-size=\"28\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">The anatomy of</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"175\" font-size=\"28\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">a good argument</text>\n  <circle cx=\"20\" cy=\"186\" r=\"12\" fill=\"#C0522E\" opacity=\"0.15\" />\n  <circle cx=\"20\" cy=\"186\" r=\"12\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" opacity=\"1\" stroke=\"#C0522E\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"191\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#C0522E\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">R</text>\n  <text x=\"38\" y=\"183\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Rakis</text>\n  <text x=\"38\" y=\"197\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Apr 9, 2026</text>\n  <line x1=\"20\" y1=\"210\" x2=\"370\" y2=\"210\" stroke=\"rgba(28,26,24,0.08)\" stroke-width=\"1\" opacity=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"256\" font-size=\"56\" fill=\"#C0522E\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">A</text>\n  <text x=\"58\" y=\"230\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.9\">n argument is a sequence of statements</text>\n  <text x=\"58\" y=\"248\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.9\">intended to establish a definite proposition.</text>\n  <text x=\"58\" y=\"266\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.9\">Not all collections of claims qualify —</text>\n  <text x=\"58\" y=\"284\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.9\">there must be structure, evidence, and</text>\n  <text x=\"58\" y=\"302\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.9\">a conclusion that the premises support.</text>\n  <rect x=\"20\" y=\"328\" width=\"350\" height=\"72\" fill=\"#F0E2DC\" rx=\"8\" opacity=\"1\" />\n  <rect x=\"20\" y=\"328\" width=\"3\" height=\"72\" fill=\"#C0522E\" rx=\"1\" opacity=\"1\" />\n  <text x=\"32\" y=\"353\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.9\">\"The strength of an argument is</text>\n  <text x=\"32\" y=\"371\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.9\">not in its volume, but in its clarity.\"</text>\n  <text x=\"32\" y=\"389\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#C0522E\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">— Aristotle, Rhetoric</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"420\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.9\">There are three classical modes: logos,</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"438\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.9\">ethos, and pathos. Modern discourse tends</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"456\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.9\">to collapse these, relying on emotional</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"474\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.9\">appeals while dressing them as logic.</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"502\" font-size=\"18\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Structure</text>\n  <line x1=\"20\" y1=\"510\" x2=\"80\" y2=\"510\" stroke=\"#C0522E\" stroke-width=\"2\" opacity=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"526\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.9\">Every valid argument has premises and a</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"544\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.9\">conclusion. The premises offer reasons;</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"562\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.9\">the conclusion is what you want accepted.</text>\n  <rect x=\"20\" y=\"596\" width=\"350\" height=\"44\" fill=\"#F5F1EB\" rx=\"10\" opacity=\"1\" />\n  <text x=\"32\" y=\"614\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#C0522E\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">✎</text>\n  <text x=\"52\" y=\"614\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">3 highlights</text>\n  <text x=\"52\" y=\"628\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Tap to review</text>\n  <text x=\"362\" y=\"621\" font-size=\"16\" fill=\"#C0522E\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"end\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">→</text>\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"753\" width=\"390\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#F5F1EB\"  opacity=\"1\" />\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"753\" width=\"136.5\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#C0522E\"  opacity=\"1\" />\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"761\" width=\"390\" height=\"83\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\"  opacity=\"1\" />\n  <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"761\" x2=\"390\" y2=\"761\" stroke=\"rgba(28,26,24,0.08)\" stroke-