\" opacity=\"1\">New Note</text>\n  <rect x=\"318\" y=\"60\" width=\"54\" height=\"26\" fill=\"#C0522E\" rx=\"13\" opacity=\"1\" />\n  <text x=\"345\" y=\"78\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Save</text>\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"92\" width=\"390\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#F5F1EB\"  opacity=\"1\" />\n  <rect x=\"10\" y=\"98\" width=\"28\" height=\"26\" fill=\"#C0522E\" rx=\"5\" opacity=\"1\" />\n  <text x=\"24\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">H1</text>\n  <text x=\"64\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">H2</text>\n  <text x=\"104\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">B</text>\n  <text x=\"144\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">I</text>\n  <text x=\"184\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">\"</text>\n  <text x=\"224\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">—</text>\n  <text x=\"264\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">·</text>\n  <text x=\"304\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Link</text>\n  <text x=\"344\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">⌘</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"174\" font-size=\"32\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.25\">Title your thought…</text>\n  <rect x=\"20\" y=\"182\" width=\"2\" height=\"36\" fill=\"#C0522E\" rx=\"1\" opacity=\"1\" />\n  <rect x=\"20\" y=\"196\" width=\"80\" height=\"26\" fill=\"#F5F1EB\" rx=\"13\" opacity=\"1\" />\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"213\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">+ Topic</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"244\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.5\">Begin writing. Every great thread starts</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"262\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.5\">with a single, honest sentence.</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"302\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Arguments are not battles to be won,</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"320\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">but conversations to be deepened. The</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"338\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">best thinkers I know ask more than they</text>\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"356\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">assert, and hold conclusions lightly.</text>\n  <rect x=\"252\" y=\"360\" width=\"2\" height=\"18\" fill=\"#C0522E\" rx=\"1\" opacity=\"1\" />\n  <text x=\"20\" y=\"390\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">38 words</text>\n  <rect x=\"20\" y=\"410\" width=\"350\" height=\"110\" fill=\"#F5F1EB\" rx=\"14\" opacity=\"1\" />\n  <text x=\"32\" y=\"432\" font-size=\"13\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Related ideas from your library</text>\n  <line x1=\"32\" y1=\"440\" x2=\"358\" y2=\"440\" stroke=\"rgba(28,26,24,0.08)\" stroke-width=\"1\" opacity=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n  <text x=\"32\" y=\"460\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">○ Steelman technique for stronger arguments</text>\n  <line x1=\"32\" y1=\"470\" x2=\"358\" y2=\"470\" stroke=\"rgba(28,26,24,0.08)\" stroke-width=\"0.5\" opacity=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n  <text x=\"32\" y=\"482\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">○ The Minto Pyramid for structured thinking</text>\n  <line x1=\"32\" y1=\"492\" x2=\"358\" y2=\"492\" stroke=\"rgba(28,26,24,0.08)\" stroke-width=\"0.5\" opacity=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n  <text x=\"32\" y=\"504\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">○ Why Socrates asked questions, not questions</text>\n  <rect x=\"20\" y=\"534\" width=\"350\" height=\"44\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" rx=\"12\" opacity=\"1\" />\n  <text x=\"32\" y=\"551\" font-size=\"16\" fill=\"#C0522E\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">⊞</text>\n  <text x=\"54\" y=\"551\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#1C1A18\" font-weight=\"500\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Use a template</text>\n  <text x=\"54\" y=\"565\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Essay, Thread, Summary, Q&A…</text>\n  <text x=\"362\" y=\"560\" font-size=\"16\" fill=\"#C0522E\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"end\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">→</text>\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"749\" width=\"390\" height=\"12\" fill=\"#FAF8F4\"  opacity=\"1\" />\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"761\" width=\"390\" height=\"83\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\"  opacity=\"1\" />\n  <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"761\" x2=\"390\" y2=\"761\" stroke=\"rgba(28,26,24,0.08)\" stroke-width=\"1\" opacity=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n  <text x=\"39\" y=\"790\" font-size=\"18\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">B</text>\n  <text x=\"39\" y=\"808\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Library</text>\n  <text x=\"117\" y=\"790\" font-size=\"18\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">E</text>\n  <text x=\"117\" y=\"808\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Explore</text>\n  <circle cx=\"195\" cy=\"792\" r=\"22\" fill=\"#C0522E\" opacity=\"1\" />\n  <text x=\"195\" y=\"798\" font-size=\"20\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" font-weight=\"300\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">+</text>\n  <text x=\"273\" y=\"790\" font-size=\"18\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">C</text>\n  <text x=\"273\" y=\"808\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Collections</text>\n  <text x=\"351\" y=\"790\" font-size=\"18\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Georgia, serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">P</text>\n  <text x=\"351\" y=\"808\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#6B6560\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"system-ui\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Profile</text>\n</svg>",
